Title: Yousaf
Writer: Joseph Weisberg (creator), Stephen Schiff, Stuart Zicherman
Actors: Keri Russell, Matthew Rhys, Annet Mahendru, Susan Misner
Plot: A new mission with international stakes has Philip calling on Annelise for assistance just as an old foe returns to D.C. with a vendetta. Stan makes a discovery that could put the FBI hot on the trail of illegals.
